"{\"uid\": \"theinertia.com-surf-surf-trip-journalists-olympic-final\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"The author, basking in the perks.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 33, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The author\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 10}, {\"ngram\": \"the perks\", \"from\": 23, \"to\": 32}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Photo: Carlos Barria Before leaving to cover the 2024 Olympics in Tahiti,I penneda storyon my blog posing a question of utmost importance: Will I get to surf?\", \"from\": 34, \"to\": 193, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 101, \"end\": 107, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.951459931545879e-17, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Carlos Barria\", \"from\": 41, \"to\": 54}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympics\", \"from\": 79, \"to\": 96}, {\"ngram\": \"my blog\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 132}, {\"ngram\": \"a question\", \"from\": 140, \"to\": 150}, {\"ngram\": \"utmost importance\", \"from\": 154, \"to\": 171}, {\"ngram\": \"surf\", \"from\": 187, \"to\": 191}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have worked a number of surf events over the years (formerly on the organizer's side) to know that surfing is not often in the cards.\", \"from\": 194, \"to\": 329, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a number\", \"from\": 208, \"to\": 216}, {\"ngram\": \"surf events\", \"from\": 220, \"to\": 231}, {\"ngram\": \"the years\", \"from\": 237, \"to\": 246}, {\"ngram\": \"the organizer's side\", \"from\": 260, \"to\": 280}, {\"ngram\": \"surfing\", \"from\": 295, \"to\": 302}, {\"ngram\": \"the cards\", \"from\": 319, \"to\": 328}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, I have a formula that computes how often I will get to surf on these trips.\", \"from\": 330, \"to\": 414, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 333, \"to\": 337}, {\"ngram\": \"a formula\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 355}, {\"ngram\": \"these trips\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 413}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I ask myself three questions: Can I walk to the wave?\", \"from\": 415, \"to\": 468, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"three questions\", \"from\": 428, \"to\": 443}, {\"ngram\": \"the wave\", \"from\": 459, \"to\": 467}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If not, do I have some type of transportation?\", \"from\": 469, \"to\": 515, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some type\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 496}, {\"ngram\": \"transportation\", \"from\": 500, \"to\": 514}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And is sunrise early enough to allow for a pre-comp session?\", \"from\": 516, \"to\": 576, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a pre-comp session\", \"from\": 557, \"to\": 575}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Tahiti, the waves were mainly outer reefs, I did not have a car, and first light was around 6 a.m.\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 679, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 581, \"end\": 587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.951459931545879e-17, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the waves\", \"from\": 589, \"to\": 598}, {\"ngram\": \"outer reefs\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 622}, {\"ngram\": \"a car\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 644}, {\"ngram\": \"first light\", \"from\": 650, \"to\": 661}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When I plugged all this into the formula, the answer was, \\\"probably not going to surf much.\\\"\", \"from\": 680, \"to\": 772, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the formula\", \"from\": 709, \"to\": 720}, {\"ngram\": \"the answer\", \"from\": 722, \"to\": 732}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, the fact that the Olympics only needed four to five days to run was one factor that worked in my favor.\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 885, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 790}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 808}, {\"ngram\": \"four to five days\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 838}, {\"ngram\": \"one factor\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 860}, {\"ngram\": \"my favor\", \"from\": 876, \"to\": 884}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unfazed by the odds, I brought two boards.\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 928, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the odds\", \"from\": 897, \"to\": 905}, {\"ngram\": \"two boards\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 927}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When I worked at the 2020 Olympics in Japan, I essentially did not surf at all during the event.\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 1026, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 968, \"end\": 973, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.8769619201899648, \"rank\": 0.14030036584695052, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2020 Olympics\", \"from\": 947, \"to\": 964}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1025}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the day after the Olympics, when all the competitors had jetted home, there was an epic day of offshore tubes for the staff.\", \"from\": 1027, \"to\": 1155, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1045, \"to\": 1057}, {\"ngram\": \"all the competitors\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1083}, {\"ngram\": \"jetted home\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1099}, {\"ngram\": \"an epic day\", \"from\": 1111, \"to\": 1122}, {\"ngram\": \"offshore tubes\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1140}, {\"ngram\": \"the staff\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1154}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I got one barrel that I still remember.\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1195, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one barrel\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1172}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I learned it's better to eat the board fees and not surf than to experience the crippling FOMO of missing an epic day of waves if the opportunity arose.\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1351, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the board fees\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1242}, {\"ngram\": \"the crippling FOMO\", \"from\": 1275, \"to\": 1293}, {\"ngram\": \"an epic day\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1316}, {\"ngram\": \"waves\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1325}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1344}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The first three days of the 2024 Olympic window were all work, but when the swell got huge and messy and the wind turned onshore, the event was called off.\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1508, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The first three days\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1373}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympic window\", \"from\": 1377, \"to\": 1400}, {\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1414}, {\"ngram\": \"the swell\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1434}, {\"ngram\": \"the wind\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1466}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1492}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the same time, Teahupo'o's little novelty river mouth turned on.\", \"from\": 1509, \"to\": 1576, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1525}, {\"ngram\": \"Teahupo'o's little novelty river mouth\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1565}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was my first chance to get in the water.\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1620, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my first chance\", \"from\": 1584, \"to\": 1599}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1619}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The reef pass at Teahupo'o is about 800 feet wide - just big enough to allow the energy of a huge swell to pass through and grace the cobblestone river mouth in town.\", \"from\": 1622, \"to\": 1788, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The reef pass\", \"from\": 1622, \"to\": 1635}, {\"ngram\": \"Teahupo'o\", \"from\": 1639, \"to\": 1648}, {\"ngram\": \"the energy\", \"from\": 1699, \"to\": 1709}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge swell\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1725}, {\"ngram\": \"the cobblestone river mouth\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1779}, {\"ngram\": \"town\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1787}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By the time the double overhead waves at Teahupo'o filter through the pass, they are waist- to chest-high, creating a fun right that even provides little tube sections before running into the beach.\", \"from\": 1789, \"to\": 1987, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 1800}, {\"ngram\": \"the double overhead waves\", \"from\": 1801, \"to\": 1826}, {\"ngram\": \"the pass\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1863}, {\"ngram\": \"a fun right\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 1916}, {\"ngram\": \"little tube sections\", \"from\": 1936, \"to\": 1956}, {\"ngram\": \"the beach\", \"from\": 1977, \"to\": 1986}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the competition off and a nice right breaking in town, as you might imagine, it was extremely crowded from dawn to dusk.\", \"from\": 1989, \"to\": 2114, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2009}, {\"ngram\": \"town\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2047}, {\"ngram\": \"dawn\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2105}, {\"ngram\": \"dusk\", \"from\": 2109, \"to\": 2113}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Faces in the lineup varied from eight-year-old Teahupo'o groms to world champions to event staff to journalists like myself.\", \"from\": 2115, \"to\": 2239, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Faces\", \"from\": 2115, \"to\": 2120}, {\"ngram\": \"the lineup\", \"from\": 2124, \"to\": 2134}, {\"ngram\": \"eight-year-old Teahupo'o groms\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2177}, {\"ngram\": \"world champions\", \"from\": 2181, \"to\": 2196}, {\"ngram\": \"event staff\", \"from\": 2200, \"to\": 2211}, {\"ngram\": \"journalists\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2226}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I spotted Carissa Moore, Alan Cleland, Molly Picklum, Caity Simmers, and Caroline Marks tearing the tiny walls to shreds.\", \"from\": 2240, \"to\": 2361, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2250, \"end\": 2263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carissa_Moore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carissa Moore\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carissa_Moore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carissa_Moore\"}, {\"begin\": 2270, \"end\": 2277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Burton_Cleland\", \"score\": 0.9997670694133795, \"rank\": 0.00021134851804060408, \"text\": \"Cleland\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Burton_Cleland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Burton_Cleland\"}, {\"begin\": 2279, \"end\": 2284, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molly_Hayes\", \"score\": 0.9999999999790816, \"rank\": 2.1277906593849996e-11, \"text\": \"Molly\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molly_Hayes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Molly_Hayes\"}, {\"begin\": 2313, \"end\": 2327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Marks\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Caroline Marks\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Marks\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Caroline_Marks\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Caity Simmers\", \"from\": 2294, \"to\": 2307}, {\"ngram\": \"the tiny walls\", \"from\": 2336, \"to\": 2350}, {\"ngram\": \"shreds\", \"from\": 2354, \"to\": 2360}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I paddled out at dusk on Tuesday, then dawn and dusk on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 2363, \"to\": 2429, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"dusk\", \"from\": 2380, \"to\": 2384}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday\", \"from\": 2388, \"to\": 2395}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 2419, \"to\": 2428}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The locals were very welcoming, but when the sets came it was clear that they were not for foreigners.\", \"from\": 2430, \"to\": 2532, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The locals\", \"from\": 2430, \"to\": 2440}, {\"ngram\": \"the sets\", \"from\": 2471, \"to\": 2479}, {\"ngram\": \"foreigners\", \"from\": 2521, \"to\": 2531}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One pre-teen on a blue soft-top easily matched the wave total of the rest of the 25-person lineup combined by himself.\", \"from\": 2533, \"to\": 2651, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One pre\", \"from\": 2533, \"to\": 2540}, {\"ngram\": \"teen\", \"from\": 2541, \"to\": 2545}, {\"ngram\": \"a blue soft-top\", \"from\": 2549, \"to\": 2564}, {\"ngram\": \"the wave total\", \"from\": 2580, \"to\": 2594}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 2598, \"to\": 2606}, {\"ngram\": \"the 25-person lineup\", \"from\": 2610, \"to\": 2630}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I took the scraps and looked for waves that swung deep or wide.\", \"from\": 2652, \"to\": 2715, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the scraps\", \"from\": 2659, \"to\": 2669}, {\"ngram\": \"waves\", \"from\": 2685, \"to\": 2690}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was good to get wet, but the novelty was wearing off with the Olympic crowds.\", \"from\": 2716, \"to\": 2796, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the novelty\", \"from\": 2744, \"to\": 2755}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic crowds\", \"from\": 2777, \"to\": 2795}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I longed for something more.\", \"from\": 2797, \"to\": 2825, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2810, \"to\": 2819}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My eyes turned to the outer reefs.\", \"from\": 2826, \"to\": 2860, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My eyes\", \"from\": 2826, \"to\": 2833}, {\"ngram\": \"the outer reefs\", \"from\": 2844, \"to\": 2859}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Thursday the competition resumed and I returned to my coverage routine, talking to athletes in the mixed zone and smacking a keyboard in the media center.\", \"from\": 2862, \"to\": 3019, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Thursday\", \"from\": 2865, \"to\": 2873}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 2874, \"to\": 2889}, {\"ngram\": \"my coverage routine\", \"from\": 2916, \"to\": 2935}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2948, \"to\": 2956}, {\"ngram\": \"the mixed zone\", \"from\": 2960, \"to\": 2974}, {\"ngram\": \"a keyboard\", \"from\": 2988, \"to\": 2998}, {\"ngram\": \"the media center\", \"from\": 3002, \"to\": 3018}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After nearly a week working in Tahiti, a camaraderie formed among the journalists at my table.\", \"from\": 3020, \"to\": 3114, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3051, \"end\": 3057, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.951459931545879e-17, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nearly a week\", \"from\": 3026, \"to\": 3039}, {\"ngram\": \"a camaraderie\", \"from\": 3059, \"to\": 3072}, {\"ngram\": \"the journalists\", \"from\": 3086, \"to\": 3101}, {\"ngram\": \"my table\", \"from\": 3105, \"to\": 3113}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even though technically we compete for readers, clicks and engagement, we bonded over the common line of work that we'd chosen.\", \"from\": 3115, \"to\": 3242, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"readers\", \"from\": 3154, \"to\": 3161}, {\"ngram\": \"clicks\", \"from\": 3163, \"to\": 3169}, {\"ngram\": \"engagement\", \"from\": 3174, \"to\": 3184}, {\"ngram\": \"the common line\", \"from\": 3201, \"to\": 3216}, {\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 3220, \"to\": 3224}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Across from me at the table satLincoln Feast, a Kiwi journalist withReuters.\", \"from\": 3244, \"to\": 3320, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3292, \"end\": 3296, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealanders\", \"score\": 0.7341395748482005, \"rank\": 0.3621289687132988, \"text\": \"Kiwi\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealanders\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealanders\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the table\", \"from\": 3262, \"to\": 3271}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To my left satDashel Pierson, associate editor ofSURFER (and former staffer atThe Inertia).\", \"from\": 3321, \"to\": 3412, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3342, \"end\": 3349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierson_College\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 8.61753067726333e-13, \"text\": \"Pierson\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierson_College\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierson_College\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"associate editor ofSURFER\", \"from\": 3351, \"to\": 3376}, {\"ngram\": \"former staffer\", \"from\": 3382, \"to\": 3396}, {\"ngram\": \"atThe Inertia\", \"from\": 3397, \"to\": 3410}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Diagonal to me was Pablo Zanocchi, the founder of the Spanish language siteDuke Surf.\", \"from\": 3413, \"to\": 3498, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pablo Zanocchi\", \"from\": 3432, \"to\": 3446}, {\"ngram\": \"the founder\", \"from\": 3448, \"to\": 3459}, {\"ngram\": \"the Spanish language\", \"from\": 3463, \"to\": 3483}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We shared stories about writing assignments and surf trips around the world.\", \"from\": 3499, \"to\": 3575, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"stories\", \"from\": 3509, \"to\": 3516}, {\"ngram\": \"assignments\", \"from\": 3531, \"to\": 3542}, {\"ngram\": \"surf\", \"from\": 3547, \"to\": 3551}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 3565, \"to\": 3574}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We used our combined decades of surf knowledge to factcheck each other and bounce ideas around.\", \"from\": 3576, \"to\": 3671, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our combined decades\", \"from\": 3584, \"to\": 3604}, {\"ngram\": \"surf knowledge\", \"from\": 3608, \"to\": 3622}, {\"ngram\": \"ideas\", \"from\": 3658, \"to\": 3663}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Pablo is a surf encyclopedia.)\", \"from\": 3672, \"to\": 3703, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pablo\", \"from\": 3673, \"to\": 3678}, {\"ngram\": \"a surf encyclopedia\", \"from\": 3682, \"to\": 3701}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And Dashel would test my reaction to debatably inappropriate metaphors he inserted into his stories that included terms like \\\"muffin tops\\\" and \\\"edging\\\" (Google it).\", \"from\": 3704, \"to\": 3868, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dashel\", \"from\": 3708, \"to\": 3714}, {\"ngram\": \"my reaction\", \"from\": 3726, \"to\": 3737}, {\"ngram\": \"debatably inappropriate metaphors\", \"from\": 3741, \"to\": 3774}, {\"ngram\": \"his stories\", \"from\": 3792, \"to\": 3803}, {\"ngram\": \"terms\", \"from\": 3818, \"to\": 3823}, {\"ngram\": \"muffin tops\", \"from\": 3830, \"to\": 3841}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We'd also joke about who would win the journalist heat.\", \"from\": 3870, \"to\": 3925, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the journalist heat\", \"from\": 3905, \"to\": 3924}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Stab'sMichael Ciaramellawas the obvious answer and thus excluded from these hypothetical debates.)\", \"from\": 3926, \"to\": 4025, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Stab'sMichael\", \"from\": 3927, \"to\": 3940}, {\"ngram\": \"the obvious answer\", \"from\": 3955, \"to\": 3973}, {\"ngram\": \"these hypothetical debates\", \"from\": 3997, \"to\": 4023}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But when the fourth day of competition wrapped and Friday was called a lay day in advance, we started to think we were due to make that journalist heat a reality.\", \"from\": 4026, \"to\": 4188, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fourth day\", \"from\": 4035, \"to\": 4049}, {\"ngram\": \"competiti