rd to distinguish where to hit the lip.\", \"from\": 5888, \"to\": 6030, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Waist-high lefts\", \"from\": 5888, \"to\": 5904}, {\"ngram\": \"the occasional chest-high set\", \"from\": 5910, \"to\": 5939}, {\"ngram\": \"the pass\", \"from\": 5953, \"to\": 5961}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 5967, \"to\": 5972}, {\"ngram\": \"the lip\", \"from\": 6022, \"to\": 6029}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pablo arrived in the second boat shuttle and hooted as I did a mediocre, backside snap typical of a washed-up, 30-something surfer like myself.\", \"from\": 6031, \"to\": 6174, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pablo\", \"from\": 6031, \"to\": 6036}, {\"ngram\": \"the second boat shuttle\", \"from\": 6048, \"to\": 6071}, {\"ngram\": \"backside\", \"from\": 6104, \"to\": 6112}, {\"ngram\": \"a washed-up, 30-something surfer\", \"from\": 6129, \"to\": 6161}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For hours, Lincoln, Dashel, Pablo, an event photographer, an ISA executive, and I traded off waves.\", \"from\": 6176, \"to\": 6275, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6187, \"end\": 6194, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abraham_Lincoln\", \"score\": 0.9994965597566412, \"rank\": 0.0005036938235289146, \"text\": \"Lincoln\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abraham_Lincoln\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abraham_Lincoln\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hours\", \"from\": 6180, \"to\": 6185}, {\"ngram\": \"Dashel\", \"from\": 6196, \"to\": 6202}, {\"ngram\": \"Pablo\", \"from\": 6204, \"to\": 6209}, {\"ngram\": \"an event photographer\", \"from\": 6211, \"to\": 6232}, {\"ngram\": \"an ISA executive\", \"from\": 6234, \"to\": 6250}, {\"ngram\": \"waves\", \"from\": 6269, \"to\": 6274}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was no hassling; just a simple rotation.\", \"from\": 6276, \"to\": 6322, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no hassling\", \"from\"